<emphasis box="[520,699,298,322]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="22">Kedestes heathi</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Hancock and Gardiner" box="[704,1039,298,323]" firstAuthor="Hancock" pageId="23" pageNumber="22" pagination="105 - 123" refId="ref27684" refString="Hancock, D. L., and A. J. Gardiner. 1982. The Kedestes nerva group of species (Lepidoptera: Hesperiidae). Arnoldia Zimbabwe 9 (8): 105 - 123." type="journal article" year="1982">Hancock and Gardiner, 1982</bibRefCitation>
